videos.headline: Iowa State adds to blowout lead with pick-six
videos.description: Iowa State DB Kamari Cotton-Moya intercepts Patrick Mahomes' pass and races 48 yards into the end zone for the pick-six, giving the Cyclones a 42-3 lead over the Red Raiders.
